        },
        {
            "id": 6318762,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 福懋科(8131)大漲7.06%，報72.8元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>福懋科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8131:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8131\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8131-TW</a>)22日11:24股價上漲4.8元，報72.8元，漲幅7.06%，成交11,085張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>福懋科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8131:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8131\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8131-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為接受委託各型積體電路之封裝、測試與模組之加工及研究開發業務。CC01080電子零組件製造業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲0.89%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.98%，股價波動與大盤表現同步。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+568 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-306 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+406 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+468 張</li> <li>融資增減：-324 張</li> <li>融券增減：-243 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6318762",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 11:24:40",
